PRIVACY POLICY FOR MOODIFY
Last updated: November 30, 2024

This Privacy Policy explains how Moodify (the “App,” “we,” “our,” or “us”) handles your data when you use our application.

Questions or concerns?
If you have any questions or concerns about this policy, please contact us at: szymolivtech@gmail.com.

Key Highlights
Personal data collected: Moodify does not collect any personal data.
Ads with AdMob: We use Google AdMob to display ads, which may collect data such as your device’s advertising ID.
Data security: No user data is stored or shared by Moodify.
Recommended age: Moodify is designed for users aged 13 and above.
1. DATA COLLECTED
Data you provide
Moodify does not request or collect any sensitive or personal information directly from users.

Automatic data collection by third parties
When you use Moodify, third-party services like Google AdMob may collect data such as:

Your device's unique advertising ID (IDFA on iOS, AAID on Android).
This data is used to provide personalized ads. For more details, please review Google’s privacy policy here.

2. HOW WE USE YOUR INFORMATION
Moodify integrates third-party advertising services to:

Display ads within the app.
Financially support the app's development.
No data collected is used by us to identify users.

3. LEGAL BASIS FOR DATA PROCESSING
Moodify adheres to applicable data protection laws, including the GDPR:

Consent: By using the app, you consent to data collection by third-party advertisers.
You can disable personalized ads in your device settings at any time.
4. TARGET AUDIENCE
Moodify is intended for users aged 13 and above, in compliance with Google AdMob advertising policies.

5. HOW WE PROTECT YOUR DATA
Although we do not store any user data, third-party services we use implement their own security measures to protect collected data.

6. YOUR RIGHTS
You have the right to:

Disable personalized ads through your device settings.
Review Google’s privacy policy to exercise your rights over data collected by their services.
7. POLICY UPDATES
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time to comply with applicable laws. Changes will be indicated with a new "last updated" date.

Contact Us
For any questions or concerns:

Email: szymolivtech@gmail.com
